## Section-05 04-Component as Building Block

- Components are most fundamental concept in react
- Because React application entirely made of components
- Components are the Building blocks of any UI in React.

- Basically React does is to take components and draw them onto a web page or UI.
- React render a view for each component and all these view togather make up the UI.
- component a piece of UI.

- One key property of each component is that each component has it's own data,
  javascipt logic and appearance.
- each component describe what it does how it look like.

- Component name should be start with uppercase character
- Component ca be reused , nested inside each other , and pass data b/w them.

- Components Tree: shows how the component nested and how they relate one another.
  we can clearly see the relationship b/w the components.
